title: [Gyldemar Forest, Stagnant Pool]
description: Black, brackish water fills the area, a stinking topping to the mud beneath.  Dead plant matter surrounds the pool.  Whether it died due to natural causes or from drinking from the pool remains a mystery.

Black, brackish water fills the area, a stinking topping to the mud beneath, which doesn't improve in appearance in the moonlight.  Dead plant matter surrounds the pool.  Whether it died due to natural causes or from drinking from the pool remains a mystery.
